Package: fixes
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Creating and Visualizing Fixed Effects Event Study Models
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Yosuke", "Abe",
      email = "yosuke.abe0507@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: This package provides functions for creating, analyzing, and visualizing event study models using fixed effects regression. It includes tools for generating lead and lag variables and producing plots with ggplot2.
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports:
    dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    fixest,
    broom,
    tibble,
    rlang
